Commentary: beauty! Exceptional bowling. Malik reviews the out decision. A big noise, was it bat on pad, or bat on ball? Hotspot has nothing. This is interesting. There is a big spike before the ball reaches the bat, which may indicate that the bat clipped the pad. But that doesn't mean there is no bat on ball. In this case, it was just bat on pad. The back flap was moved forward with the bat. Good use of the review from Malik, called for it immediately.
